-created-weak-shaytan\/","url_meta":{"origin":32330,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Desire: Humankind was created vulnerable to Satan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 7, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen Allah formed Adam in Paradise, He left him as long as He willed. Satan\u00a0walked around him, looking at him. When he saw what was within mankind, he knew they were created with a disposition\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":769,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/10\/hearts-fingers-rahman\/","url_meta":{"origin":32330,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Qulub: Allah directs the hearts as He wills","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 10, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the hearts of the children of Adam, all of them, are between the two fingers of the Merciful as one heart. He directs them wherever He wills. O Allah, the Director of the hearts,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3449,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/06\/28\/all-people-children-adam\/","url_meta":{"origin":32330,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Adam: All people are the children of Adam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"